commit.message: Fixed a Bug in Transaction::isSuccessful() : check if $response has data array before checking if its an object
Updated ReadMe: Documented the new method amountEquals() added to the Transaction Resource Class
Did a test to see Transaction::amountEquals() works
Created a method to confirm transaction amount amountEquals() and did some documentation
Created a method to debug string values printStr()
Added Accessor and Mutator for _errorMessages private property: Matscode\Paystack\Base
Fix verify method to return false instead of throwong an \Exception if not successful
Major Feature Release: Paystack Transaction Resource
